summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of Lots 13 and 14, Block 66, Replat of Blocks 65, 66, 158, 159, 160, 161 and 163, Gilman Park, with respect to Use District, and for the rezoning of Lots 1 and 2, Block 3, Pratt's Orchard Addition, with respect to Height and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto two new sections numbered 2-38 and 17-23.
